                    <h2 class="fs-2">Endpoints</h2>
                    <p class="fs-4">PotterHead API has 3 endpoints:</p>
                    <ul>
                              <li>
                                <p class="fs-5">Characters - <code>/api/characters</code>, This endpoint retrives all characters and their dertails</p>
                                <a href="/api/characters" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">Check Out</a>
                              </li>
                              <br>
                              <li>
                                <p class="fs-5">Spells - <code>/api/spells</code>, This endpoint retrives all spells and their usage.</p>
                                 <a href="/api/spells" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">Check Out</a>  
                              </li>
                              <br>
                              <li>
                                <p class="fs-5">Potions - <code>/api/potions</code>, This endpoint retrives all magical potions and their incredients.</p>
                                 <a href="/api/potions" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">Check Out</a>
                              </li>
                    </ul>
